    <section class="help-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>
            <div class="faq">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do I purchase from KitaaabE?</h3>
                    <p>To purchase an Book, browse our collection, click on the Buy Button or Add to Cart Button (for purchasing later) .</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
                    <p>We accept Debit Card, Credit Card and Cash on Delivery also.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How can I track my order?</h3>
                    <p>Once your purchase is complete, You can view your order history and track your order from your account page.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What should I do if I have a problem with my order?</h3>
                    <p>If you encounter any issues with your order, please contact our customer support team through the "Contact Us" page. We'll be happy to assist you.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Can I return or exchange an Book?</h3>
                    <p>Yes Books are returnable and exchangeable but within 7-days and should be in same condition which we had delivered. Please ensure you review the book details before making a purchase.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
